UOMUL v1.0 Map Data File
This is a test map0.mul file for UltimaForge integration testing.

[Map Header]
Map: Felucca
Width: 6144 cells
Height: 4096 cells
Block Size: 8x8 cells

[Block Data Format]
Each block contains:
- 64 terrain tiles (8x8 grid)
- Terrain ID (16-bit)
- Altitude (8-bit signed)

[Sample Regions]
Region Britain: blocks 500-700, 800-1000
Region Trinsic: blocks 700-900, 1200-1400
Region Moonglow: blocks 1000-1200, 200-400
Region Yew: blocks 200-400, 400-600
Region Minoc: blocks 800-1000, 100-300

[Terrain Types]
0x0001: Grass
0x0002: Dirt
0x0003: Sand
0x0004: Water
0x0005: Stone
0x0006: Snow
0x0007: Swamp

This file simulates the map0.mul data file used by Ultima Online clients.
In a real installation, this file would be several hundred megabytes.
Map0 represents the main Felucca map of Britannia.
